		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2c62d3" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2c62d3">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人扔出纯水制成的标枪，落地造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%</span><span>伤害，可连续施放3次；<br/></span><span color="#9999ff">半幻人强化：</span><span>伤害倍率提升，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="447" width="408" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人用左手拍向玩家，造成<span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人旋转纯水制成的榔锤，进行3次攻击，依次造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%,62.5%,65%</span><span>伤害；<br/></span><span color="#9999ff">半幻人强化：</span><span>伤害倍率提升，挥舞造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%,92.5%,95%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="671" width="422" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人溅起澜海激潮，在场地内下起小雨，造成<span color="#7fbfff">20%</span><span>伤害；溅起的潮水凝结成3-4把水枪，并一起在自身周围降下，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="440" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">每12.5s，水形幻人会在随机位置召唤一只<span textDecoration="underline">半幻人</span><span>，最多存在3个；<br/>在战斗中水形幻人会随机吸收一只半幻人，获得强化：</span><span color="#ffcdbf">全抗性提升45%</span><span>，伤害倍率提升30%，施放1-2个技能后结束</span><span color="#cebfff">(纳齐森科鲁兹无需吸收，原地强化)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="959" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">半幻人发射一枚弱追踪性的水弹，造成半幻人<span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>攻击力的伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="959" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">半幻人用一侧的肢体击地，造成半幻人<span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>攻击力的伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人挥舞纯水制成的短刀，进行2次攻击，依次造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%,65%</span><span>伤害；<br/></span><span color="#9999ff">半幻人强化：</span><span>伤害倍率提升，挥舞造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%,95%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
