		<RichText x="66" y="1068" width="434" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">半幻人：<span color="#7fbfff">1水</span><span>盾，击破后立即死亡，可伤害转化(4倍)；半幻人继承水形幻人20%的攻击力。</span></p>
			</content>
